title: 90L Storage Bags with Lid and Zips,3 Pack Foldable Storage Box with Reinforced Handle Thick Fabric Clear Window for Clothing Bedding Blankets, Grey
features: 【Large Capacity】：Each clothes storage bags is 90L capacity, 60x40x35cm(23.6x15.7x13.7inch).It is spacious for your comforters, blankets, pillows, plush toys, jackets or other household items. Three packs in one set and it's suitable for your daily Life.

【Premium Material】：Each storage bag is made of high-quality odorless and three-ply composite non-woven fabric and it has excellent breathability. It can be reused, promote ventilation, and effectively prevent dust, odors, and mold. It can effectively protect your items.

【Reinforced Handle】：Our storage bag’s handle is stitching with stronger polyester thread. Reinforced seams are also implemented for added strength. Ensure the handle will not break off during use.You can safely transport it from one place to another.

【Sturdy Zipper】：The zipper is made of sturdy stainless steel. Each storage bag is equipped with high-quality smooth zippers and a sturdy two-way zipper closure for easy sliding. And with transparent windows, you can quickly find the items you need, saving time and energy.

【Versatile and Portable】:These clothing storage bags are not only perfect for organizing your bedroom wardrobe; They are also an ideal choice for organizing student dormitories, moving and tidying up, and seasonal storage. Our storage bags can be folded and reused multiple times when not in use to save space and keep your storage area organized.
